Robert Durst was arrested in March for the murder of his friend Susan Berman in 2000 . 
  Authorities found $44,000, marijuana and a revolver in his hotel room in New Orleans . 
  His lawyers say he got the money legally and it is not needed for evidence . 
  He was arrested for murder in 2000 to keep Berman from talking about the disappearance of his first wife in 1982 . 
 